title: Skillfeed Create a JavaScript Dating HTML5 App
description:
Skillfeed Create a JavaScript Dating HTML5 App


HTML5 allows you to create cross-platform apps that run on the
web, on mobile platforms such as iOS and Android, smart tv's
and a myriad of new devices coming all the time. In this course
we'll make a HTML5 responsive app prototype of a dating app
where you can search through different members and in the
process learn how to work with the DOM, JSON and more advanced
JavaScript
